      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW OLYMPUS (4) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Grade 5 winner two back at Warrnambool. Better than latest and can atone here. BLACK STATESMAN (6) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third (23.87) in a Grade 5 over 425m at Bendigo. Well placed here and should do much better. PAW LAMPADES (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.53) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Should be in this for a long way. GUITAR TANGO (8) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.",
